<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/ellie-reeves> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Ellie Reeves was appointed as Solicitor General on 6 September 2025. She was previously Minister without Portfolio at the Cabinet Office from 6 July 2024 to 6 September 2025. She was elected as the MP for Lewisham West and East Dulwich in 2024 and was previously the MP for Lewisham West and Penge from 2017."@en .
